{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/gstring\/naturalnocasecmpto(_:)"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","externalID":"s:10SwiftGodot7GStringC18naturalnocasecmpToys5Int64VACF","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"SwiftGodot"}],"title":"naturalnocasecmpTo(_:)","roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"naturalnocasecmpTo","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10SwiftGodot7GStringC","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GString"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Int64","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int64V","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"final","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"naturalnocasecmpTo"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"_"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GString","text":"GString","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10SwiftGodot7GStringC"},{"text":") -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int64V","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int64"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"When used for sorting, natural order comparison orders sequences of numbers by the combined value of each digit as is often expected, instead of the single digit’s value. A sorted sequence of numbered strings will be ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[\"1\", \"2\", \"3\", ...]"},{"text":", not ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"[\"1\", \"10\", \"2\", \"3\", ...]"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"With different string lengths, returns "},{"code":"1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if this string is longer than the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"to"},{"type":"text","text":" string, or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"-1"},{"type":"text","text":" if shorter. Note that the length of empty strings is "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"always"}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"To get a [bool] result from a string comparison, use the "},{"code":"==","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" operator instead. See also "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"naturalcasecmpTo(to:)"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"code":"nocasecmpTo(to:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"casecmpTo(to:)"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GString\/naturalnocasecmpTo(_:)"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot","doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GString"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Performs a "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"case-insensitive"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"natural order","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" comparison to another string. Returns ","type":"text"},{"code":"-1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if less than, "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"1"},{"text":" if greater than, or ","type":"text"},{"code":"0","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if equal. “Less than” or “greater than” are determined by the "},{"type":"text","text":"Unicode code points"},{"type":"text","text":" of each string, which roughly matches the alphabetical order. Internally, lowercase characters are converted to uppercase for the comparison."}],"references":{"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/GString":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"GString","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/gstring","role":"symbol","title":"GString","type":"topic","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"GString"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A built-in type for strings."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GString","kind":"symbol"},"doc://SwiftGodot/documentation/SwiftGodot/GString/naturalnocasecmpTo(_:)":{"title":"naturalnocasecmpTo(_:)","abstract":[{"text":"Performs a ","type":"text"},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"case-insensitive","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"natural order"}]},{"type":"text","text":" comparison to another string. Returns "},{"code":"-1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if less than, "},{"code":"1","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" if greater than, or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"text":" if equal. “Less than” or “greater than” are determined by the ","type":"text"},{"text":"Unicode code points","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" of each string, which roughly matches the alphabetical order. Internally, lowercase characters are converted to uppercase for the comparison."}],"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"naturalnocasecmpTo"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10SwiftGodot7GStringC","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GString"},{"kind":"text","text":") -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5Int64V","text":"Int64"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/swiftgodot\/gstring\/naturalnocasecmpto(_:)","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/SwiftGodot\/documentation\/SwiftGodot\/GString\/naturalnocasecmpTo(_:)","t